These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, onion
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person eating onion is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Food   | onion       | eggplant     | grapes    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Sport         | badminton | skateboarding | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different games are played: poker, chess, whist
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, collecting, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, teacher
1. the teacher is the person playing whist##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the teacher##3
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the musician is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the teacher is in an even position##4
6. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game    | poker     | whist  | chess  |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | chess    |
| Job     | dancer      | teacher    | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, plum
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
City: boston, berlin, london
1. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to london is the person eating apple##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | apple         | plum     | kiwi   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| City         | london | boston | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, reading
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda  | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby        | reading | puzzles  | video-games |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | snake         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, satire, time-travel
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, classical
1. the american is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
2. the australian is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | romance  | satire  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Music-Genre           | r&b  | classical    | hip-hop    |

