.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, singing
City: new-york, rome, berlin
1. the person drinking cola is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | sprite  | cola  | milk        |
| Hobby       | singing | chess | board-games |
| City   | new-york    | rome   | berlin   |

