.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, collecting, rock-climbing
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, polish, thai
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
3. the polish is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
4. the pakistani is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | collecting | camping | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | thai       | polish  | pakistani     |
| Job           | dressmaker     | social-worker     | fisherman          |

