2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the musician##1
5. the electrician is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping     | hiking   |
| Job           | mechanic  | electrician | musician |
| Cigar   | old-henry | ritmeester     | fonseca |

