.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, pilot, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, october, november
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the pilot is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | pilot      | paramedic | social-worker |
| Birthday     | october | april      | november           |
| Sport   | water-polo | climbing  | volleyball    |

