.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, sudoku
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, musical
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, ship, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person watching documentary movies##2
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching musical movies is the person driving the ship##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
7. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | sudoku      | collecting | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime      | musical    |
| Transport           | jet-ski      | boat        | ship       |

 